  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 400&deg;F/ Gas 6</p>\r\n<p>Slice the <strong>cucumber</strong> finely&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>sliced cucumber</strong> to a sieve&nbsp;and sprinkle with a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Give the <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>cucumber</strong> a good mix up and leave to drain over the sink for 10 min&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Lato; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1228.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1228.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1228.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1228.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1228.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>sweet potatoes</strong> (skins on) into large bite-sized pieces</p>\r\n<p>Add the<strong> sweet potatoes</strong>&nbsp;to a baking tray, drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and season with a generous pinch of&nbsp;<strong>salt</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sprinkle with the<strong> nigella seeds</strong></p>\r\n<p>Place the tray in the oven for 25 min or until they're cooked through and starting to crisp</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1228.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1228.-step-2-x400.jpg",
