            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1228.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1228.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Combine 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>boiled water</strong> in a bowl until dissolved&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once dissolved, add the <strong>apple cider vinegar </strong>&ndash;&nbsp;this is your<strong> pickling liquor&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and slice the<strong> shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1228.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
