          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rinse the <strong>sliced cucumber</strong> under <strong>cold water</strong>&nbsp;to remove any excess salt and give it a good squeeze&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the<strong> sliced cucumber</strong> and <strong>shallot</strong> to the <strong>pickling liquor</strong>&nbsp;and set aside until serving&nbsp;</p>",
